{"tid":1778094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣大選前香港人應該集會","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T13:18:49.000Z","uid":93141,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8930310b61935b45e2e42e266728c2d482b33389","tid":1778094,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"但主題應該係反共，多謝台灣支持，支持佢地既民主自由，甚至台灣獨立etc<br />\n<br />\n而唔好直接話支持民進黨/蔡英文，唔好將共同既理想單單同黨掛鉤，現實地講，好多台灣人將黨爭睇得好污糟。唔好令對家認為我地係操縱選舉，亦唔好自我實現人血饅頭呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n或者轉個角度，假如外國點名支持泛民黨/本土黨，<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;叫&ldquo;</span>你區議會立法會投邊個，唔同光譜都可能有反彈。至於我地自己心入面支持蔡英文，就尊重返佢地既&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">自由選擇&ldquo;</span>，暗示都比曬，淨低既就台灣人自己<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;揀&rdquo;</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該將集會同成個國家掛鉤，將反共拉到去國家層面。<br />\n<br />\n一方面&ldquo;香港人支持台灣&ldquo;可以尊重返佢地作為國家既地位，二來將選舉本身同反送中脫鉤，三來可以尊重返香港人本身係個獨立民族既身份。<br />\n<br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反擊</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cecb56e7fcf31d5bc4846deea4be9587f0c2873b","tid":1778094,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a31054535c001ed035c5d3f3641d30a49298a87","tid":1778094,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cecb56e7fcf31d5bc4846deea4be9587f0c2873b","tid":1778094,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"樓主又唔記得轉ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edf4a1d12780d6c8268db22d429ac07a82